Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.17,0:00:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到羅德斯島
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.30,0:00:08.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼緊接著\N就請觀賞第二部份吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.17,0:00:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,~歡迎來到羅德斯島~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.61,0:00:20.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，累死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.63,0:00:24.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能從迷宮出來真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.46,0:00:27.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是為什麼我們會\N在那種地方迷路啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.57,0:00:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許是神給我們的試煉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.44,0:00:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.77,0:00:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，妮絲\N有可以使體力回復的魔法嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.64,0:00:36.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.48,0:00:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能拜託妳?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.91,0:00:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了，我試試看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.01,0:00:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了…我快累翻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.62,0:00:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大地之母的瑪法呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.35,0:00:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是怎麼樣\N那樣好呢還是這樣好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.55,0:00:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎樣呢?…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.00,0:01:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像弄錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.61,0:01:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是熱鬧呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.28,0:01:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，祭司大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.88,0:01:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅者啊…可以的話\N我有些話想特地對你們說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.28,0:01:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝，請說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.15,0:01:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是有關棒棒糖的正確舔法…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.39,0:01:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過在說之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.63,0:01:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能讓你們白白聽我講所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.43,0:01:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要先給我謝禮!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.03,0:01:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以\N這是要給龍媽媽的餅乾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.04,0:01:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是暗妖精!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.51,0:01:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然拆穿了就沒辦法了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.24,0:01:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.95,0:01:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何，這樣就抓不到我了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.48,0:01:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我記住!\N我一定要吃到那餅乾!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.75,0:01:55.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在某種意義上他是可怕的敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.56,0:01:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.32,0:01:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得在看喔
